{"id":614388,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/07/unwire-中国网军扬言到香港fb踩场反被起底个人私隐/","date":"2019-07-23T17:07:04Z","modified":"2019-07-23T17:07:04Z","title":"unwire | 中国网军扬言到香港FB踩场反被起底个人私隐","content":"<p>中国有一个名为帝吧的Facebook 群组，主力找一些意见不同的群组专页「洗版」。最近以拥护一国两制为理由到香港某FB 群组「洗版」，但极速被香港网民起底，将该拟似网军的管理员及很多重要成员所有资料，包括地址，银行帐号及余额都公开。能起底都如此深入，其实是中国网路实名制、个人信息连结及私隐保护力极低。</p>\n<p>中国有一个名为帝吧的Facebook 群组，主力找一些意见不同的群组专页「洗版」。最近以拥护一国两制为理由到香港某FB 群组「洗版」，但极速被香港网民起底，将该拟似网军的管理员及很多重要成员所有资料，包括地址，银行帐号及余额都公开。能起底都如此深入，其实是中国网路实名制、个人信息连结及私隐保护力极低。</p>\n<p>领军到香港洗版秒速被起底</p>\n<p>本来帝吧组集结在23 日晚8 点出发，有传目标是连登专页，但事前攻击了某香港群组专页，并且洗版留下多个「爱国」讯息。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_614389\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午4.36.27-547x900.png\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-614389\" class=\"wp-image-614389\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午4.36.27-547x900.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"740\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午4.36.27-547x900.png 547w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午4.36.27-547x900-182x300.png 182w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-614389\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">多个「爱国」讯息</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_614390\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午4.36.39-603x900.png\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-614390\" class=\"wp-image-614390\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午4.36.39-603x900.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"672\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午4.36.39-603x900.png 603w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午4.36.39-603x900-201x300.png 201w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-614390\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">行动poster，有人猜测目标是连登，但他们提早在某HK FB 群组中心「出手」了</p></div>\n<p>连银行户口有几多钱都看到</p>\n<p>洗版不久后便光速被香港网民起底，而且个人资料的关联性相当深，只需要有其中一项资料，就可以找出个人的所有资料，例如真实姓名、身份证号、家庭住址、手机号、QQ、财付通、支付宝、银行卡及余额全数都可以被其它人观看。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_614391\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午4.33.05-656x900.png\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-614391\" class=\"wp-image-614391\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午4.33.05-656x900.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"617\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午4.33.05-656x900.png 656w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午4.33.05-656x900-219x300.png 219w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-614391\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">图片来源：连登</p></div>\n<p><strong>被起底后团长「善意」停止洗版</strong></p>\n<p>由于多位团员那么快速被起底，该「网军」随即宣布以「不破坏香港人民群众正常生活秩序」为名停止活动。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/cDo0o3N-450x900.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-614393\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/cDo0o3N-450x900.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/cDo0o3N-450x900.png 450w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/cDo0o3N-450x900-150x300.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_614392\" style=\"width: 440px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67403415_719254781865327_371336640414613504_n-430x900.png\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-614392\" class=\"wp-image-614392 size-full\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67403415_719254781865327_371336640414613504_n-430x900.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"430\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67403415_719254781865327_371336640414613504_n-430x900.png 430w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67403415_719254781865327_371336640414613504_n-430x900-143x300.png 143w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 100vw, 430px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-614392\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">同时帝吧管理员亦公开表示，将不会再负责微博更新。</p></div>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/07/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%88%b1%e5%9b%bd%e6%9c%89%e7%bd%aa-%e6%b0%91%e9%97%b4%e7%88%b1%e5%9b%bd%e9%81%ad%e9%81%87%e9%87%8d%e5%a4%a7%e6%8c%ab%e6%8a%98/\">【立此存照】爱国有罪 “民间爱国”遭遇重大挫折</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67174957_454065068657972_3563568235603296256_n-437x900.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-614394\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67174957_454065068657972_3563568235603296256_n-437x900.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"437\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67174957_454065068657972_3563568235603296256_n-437x900.jpg 437w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67174957_454065068657972_3563568235603296256_n-437x900-146x300.jpg 146w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 437px) 100vw, 437px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67156645_358453191500625_2821728552091648000_n-768x576.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-614395\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67156645_358453191500625_2821728552091648000_n-768x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67156645_358453191500625_2821728552091648000_n-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/67156645_358453191500625_2821728552091648000_n-768x576-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_614396\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/c9D0teM.png\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-614396\" class=\"wp-image-614396\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/c9D0teM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"326\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/c9D0teM.png 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/c9D0teM-300x217.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/c9D0teM-768x557.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-614396\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">被报名参军</p></div>\n<p><strong>中国个人信息管理不足是问题所在</strong></p>\n<p>对于如此详尽的个人私稳被揭露，很多会员都相当惊讶。亦有人看到问题在所，由于中国很多网站在出售个人资料是没有安全性可言，只要花钱就能获得详细个人资料。其实小编觉得网络实名制再加上个人信息的详尽连结，必需要有极好的保密措施。唯中国对于个人信息规管不足，让任何企业或组织都可轻易获得并查阅「完全版」个人私隐。例如公司聘请员工时，可以轻易了解该名人士的关键记录，员工亦可以了解公司过去的资料，此情况到底是好是坏，对个人私隐资料安全方面，确实成为一个值得关注的问题。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午5.51.50-768x105.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-614397\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午5.51.50-768x105.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"75\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午5.51.50-768x105.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午5.51.50-768x105-300x41.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/螢幕截圖-2019-07-23-下午5.51.50-768x105-220x30.png 220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,18424],"tags":[38564,38551,10605,30038,30059,38643,8686,38526]}